{
  "sections": {
    "gp_section_607382112407913220": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "499ce0d2a860aa46a84460306ba15dca07eb09605207bc70e386b727390fc2e5_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg6A4lCuVbe_text": "Forget Collagen &amp; Retinol…<br><span style=\"color:#FFF000;\">Leading Harvard Dermatologist</span><br>Recommends THIS 10-Second Trick To Shrink Lip Lines &amp; Correct Saggy Skin.",
        "ggfsj0hhMQT_background_desktop_image_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/banner_f1e57bc1-8c5e-451f-b401-2b8b26671a72.jpg",
        "section_preload": "true"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607382112407913220"
    },
    "gp_section_607382152488682070": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "2d3bfeebbb389ca6931b2de217595116e1b139a6fb52614cb5a4837528f07711_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggAlgyIwsuu_text": "<p>Yet while Progerin is bad news, there is something simple you can do to get it under control. Something that will stop Progerin from thinning and fraying your collagen and elastin so you can once again have beautifully firm, wrinkle-free skin.</p>",
        "ggE8Gr76nNy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s1bximg.png",
        "ggLJR58Kk8u_text": "<p>A 10-second tweak to your morning routine that probably has more wrinkle-erasing and skin-tightening power than collagen and retinol combined.</p>",
        "ggM83Xc3UVl_text": "<p>To put it simply…</p>",
        "ggUpm_nIJW8_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s1img_6cc5cf3c-f383-4e86-bd1f-081ab2e53ebf.png",
        "ggcx0d-287Q_text": "<p>When the lip lines and mouth wrinkles won’t disappear, your jowls are softening and your neckline continues to droop and sag no matter what you try… There’s only one thing to blame: <strong>PROGERIN</strong>.</p>",
        "ggkfO2WC4nu_text": "<p>Progerin keeps you stuck with skin you don’t like. It makes you look older, and will leave you wondering whether your skincare routine is really doing anything.</p>",
        "ggrIT8j6Gse_text": "<p>A nasty “aging protein” that destroys the healthy collagen and elastin fibers you need to have smooth, firm, lifted skin. While also preventing healthy new skin cells from bubbling to the surface so that you look younger and healthier.</p>",
        "gguIkD8Jj0g_text": "<p>Women all over America are reporting that this 10-second trick is all they need to have smoother, firmer skin on their face, as well as a tighter, more youthful-looking neck.</p>",
        "ggwA8mnB55u_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s1img_6cc5cf3c-f383-4e86-bd1f-081ab2e53ebf.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607382152488682070"
    },
    "gp_section_607384197513872282": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "3b9aa2dfcf5b99555f215d7582a98287faef74bb8deb002a154078555c77ac4a_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-BEfuqHLw_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/dermatologist-profile_08c5fe82-ed35-462b-b49b-d9878bbcc811.png",
        "gg-BEfuqHLw_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Generated_Image_February_20_2026_-_11_38PM_copy_9926b4b9-3656-4301-a244-14f6efc2d053.png",
        "gg1KQWhMyxG_text": "<p>And the truth is, the beauty industry would prefer it if you never found out about this Progerin-reducing tweak because once you see the results for yourself, the days of you buying cream after cream will be well and truly over.</p>",
        "gg2Rc6G8LXc_text": "<p>My name is</p>",
        "gg3gLhL9HDC_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Generated_Image_February_20_2026_-_11_38PM_copy_9926b4b9-3656-4301-a244-14f6efc2d053.png",
        "gg3qqTazfO2_text": "That's Why I Made This Breakthrough Skincare Report.",
        "gg6MUVPTXNA_text": "<p><strong>Today, I'm proud to say that not only does Beverly look 15 years younger, she's actually glowing with confidence because her skin finally looks as young as she feels.</strong></p>",
        "gg7XgSzov0F_text": "<p>Despite being Korea's most sought-after dermatologist, treating A-list celebrities, and having access to every cutting-edge treatment, I was heartbroken watching women like Beverly, one of my long-time patients, struggle with premature aging.</p>",
        "gg9Svp9nc1I_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2img_29938c96-fa30-4841-a7de-cddf1b7ad193.png",
        "gg9Svp9nc1I_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2img_29938c96-fa30-4841-a7de-cddf1b7ad193.png",
        "ggABItSTyUA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2bx2hdimg.png",
        "ggCvmVWuFoM_text": "<p>Dr. Manjula Jegasothy</p>",
        "ggOOMltb1SK_text": "<p>As founder of the world-renowned<br>Korea Skin Institute and a regular speaker at the Cosmetic Surgery Forum &amp; Florida Society of Dermatologic Surgeons, I've spent the last 20 years helping women defy their years.</p>",
        "ggQXUpT8YpJ_text": "<p>What's the one thing you need to understand?</p>",
        "ggRfvt8DGjf_text": "<p>and I'm a leading dermatologist from Korea, Florida.</p>",
        "ggTKOvQiepL_text": "<p>At just 55, her face showed deep lines, sagging jowls, and a loss of firmness that made her look 15 years older than her actual age. She had tried everything -- from $500 creams to painful and risky procedures.</p>",
        "ggUZjIpONfG_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2arw.png",
        "ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_0": "<p>You do <u>not </u>need invasive surgery.</p>",
        "ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_1": "<p>You do <u>not </u>need painful injections.</p>",
        "ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_2": "<p>You do <u>not </u>need expensive laser treatments.</p>",
        "ggWTDgrNLap_childItem_3": "<p>And you don&#039;t need $500 creams...</p>",
        "ggYKI5tqYft_text": "<p>That was then.</p>",
        "ggbThhKUQwM_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s2bx3img.png",
        "ggc8pbmE8CN_text": "<p>To achieve this type of skin transformation yourself...</p>",
        "ggh4nPDO9YS_text": "<p>Best of all, I've now helped thousands of women achieve the same results... including women of EVERY age, many of whom had given up hope of ever looking youthful again.</p>",
        "ggyZsT5Jfxu_text": "<p>What you <strong>DO </strong>need is to understand one – just one – crucial discovery about aging skin, and if you do, I can practically guarantee your appearance will transform in a matter of weeks.</p>",
        "ggzadrGizPU_text": "<p>\"Every morning I'd look in the mirror and barely recognize myself,\" Beverly told me. \"I felt like I was disappearing, watching my youthful appearance slip away despite doing everything right.\"</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607384197513872282"
    },
    "gp_section_607385848459035222": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "9d6594abe25a7d2c77d9e8a7e557cd05edbd49456ac18bfe3943c15f5b423d4e_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg2S19I0igj_text": "<p><strong>Think most anti-aging creams work? &nbsp;THINK AGAIN:</strong> Many actually contain ingredients that INCREASE Progerin levels! Keep reading — because throughout this report, I'll shatter more 'beauty industry myths' just like this.</p>",
        "gg35Ax24VrF_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3bximg.png",
        "gg4bdRiR0_k_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3img1_e9422307-3f1e-4b96-9a83-80d3c2a12059.png",
        "gg6Ak-Eymez_text": "<p>For instance, what if I told you that standard anti-aging creams are USELESS against this aging protein – and a specific peptide called Progeline is actually FAR more effective?</p>",
        "ggATFYPy_dZ_text": "<p>It's actually EASY... as long as you're prepared to stop believing several myths you've heard all your life about what actually works to make your skin look and feel younger.</p>",
        "ggDGkkXzXpz_text": "The \"Aging Protein\" Called Progerin.",
        "ggG8pYyRATU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3img2.png",
        "ggL9bdTgJ3I_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3img1_e9422307-3f1e-4b96-9a83-80d3c2a12059.png",
        "ggMe3An4MfD_text": "<p>And what if I told you that French scientists discovered this \"aging protein\" by studying children with <strong>Hutchinson-Gilford Syndrome</strong>, the \"Benjamin Button\" disease that causes rapid aging?</p>",
        "ggXQZd0QHIj_text": "<p>And do you know the best part?</p>",
        "ggh4L4_ItMu_text": "<p>Much of what you're about to hear has never been shared before outside my world-renowned clinic in Korea. And it's based on ironclad scientific research from the <strong>National Human Genome Research Institute</strong> as well as my own clinical experience as a board-certified dermatologist.</p>",
        "gghF_p8Aql__text": "<p>Today, I'm going to share with you my brand new <strong>\"Anti-Progerin Protocol\"</strong> for transforming your aging skin and achieving the youthful appearance you deserve.</p>",
        "ggk-nuQkFRK_text": "<p>And what if I told you that a groundbreaking study from the <strong>Society of Cosmetic Chemists</strong> found a natural peptide that can help reduce aging Progerin levels by an astonishing 22%?</p>",
        "ggtai8EW-K-_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s3img2.png",
        "ggv5xjErSYQ_text": "<p>These statements are all 100% true and backed by science, including research from the <strong>National Human Genome Research Institute</strong> and <strong>The Advances in Dermatology Study.</strong> While they may seem unrelated, they all work because they have to do with one part of your skin...</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607385848459035222"
    },
    "gp_section_607390817165771350": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "972e88326e7aeff87f9af239daa3d50a28172b5c87c1be7d3efc3efd4365d7d8_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg5a9ub8W2Z_text": "<p>Amazingly, many of them -- like many of my patients in Korea-- look so good, people think they're 30 to 40 years younger than their actual age.</p>",
        "gg79y8yM_WH_text": "<p>It’s working for the thousands of women who come and see me at my practice every week.</p>",
        "ggEUCQTNuXz_text": "<p>It’s because they’ve discovered the secret I’m about to share with you today.</p>",
        "ggHfEAlHcKb_text": "<p>The reality is, there are thousands of women in their 50s, 60s, and 70s who look decades younger than their age.</p>",
        "ggKAPxf4Hz0_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s4img_a3418d5e-fa9f-4bc5-8a43-5c9d848a3e62.png",
        "ggWh7NH4DIL_text": "<p>I'm here to tell you that, despite what you've heard, their amazing appearance is NOT due to good luck or superior genetics.</p>",
        "ggZ9BzkhnCU_text": "<p>And I promise you, this is just the TIP of the iceberg. Looking years younger is not impossible.</p>",
        "ggeTFVi8Eu2_text": "<p>And the key to maintaining youthful, firm skin is actually based on scientific research... and something EVERYONE has access to.</p>",
        "ggfY6ei2zpb_text": "<p>And it’s working better than I could have imagined.</p>",
        "gglNo3FHQAw_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s4img_a3418d5e-fa9f-4bc5-8a43-5c9d848a3e62.png",
        "ggo30HddEAg_text": "You Guessed It, Your Progerin Levels.",
        "ggp8L0aPvyH_text": "<p>I’ve spent years studying this “hidden secret” to younger-looking skin…and even tested it on myself.</p>",
        "ggrmuvU2i0t_text": "<p>I’m sure you’ve seen women in Korea and wondered how they look decades younger than their real age…</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607390817165771350"
    },
    "gp_section_607393004713411158": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "cfd135bc4da6cd454a445d6234d35a9f7e027147b292040cb67a1b625f6c7c37_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg0TMPe4VmS_text": "<p>What they don't want you to know is that they aren't in control of your aging...YOU are.</p>",
        "gg5YMEI5zwl_text": "And Today, I Will Share This Secret... Every Detail That You Need To Know If You’re Over 30...With You.",
        "ggB9YXtmlq3_text": "<p><strong>And it all starts with Progerin control.</strong></p>",
        "ggGezG8trT7_text": "<p>Waiting for us to get desperate so they can charge us for expensive creams and treatments that only mask our aging concerns.</p>",
        "ggKIkER_mKL_text": "<p>And that the key to youthful, firm skin is actually SIMPLE... and something EVERYONE has access to.</p>",
        "ggQcA0MaGwq_text": "<p>Firstly, the waiting list to see me personally in Korea is currently over a year long. And that's with me working 6 days a week and taking almost no vacations!</p>",
        "ggZthUHEInP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s5img.png",
        "ggdXUFd4O9B_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s5img.png",
        "gghU0ILXFYa_text": "<p>Okay, on to the good news.</p>",
        "ggmLZwzA-P1_text": "<p>Once I realized the importance of controlling this aging protein, I began to look at skin aging in a completely different way.</p>",
        "ggnaf3mekjw_text": "<p>Why am I doing this?</p>",
        "ggpOs3FHNdg_text": "<p>It's become obvious to me that if I'm going to reach my goal of helping the millions of women who struggle with loose and sagging skin, deep wrinkles, and uneven texture... <strong>I need to spread the word right now about the true cause of aging skin, so women across America can finally take back control of their appearance.</strong></p>",
        "gguFSTrTkfD_text": "<p>We live in a world where skincare companies and beauty brands don't provide real anti-aging solutions...they just provide temporary fixes...</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607393004713411158"
    },
    "gp_section_607393614816870998": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "db0e06d5098860a6f130a84e620447b9ef6fa2ca23a9cd23ac5c3848f0c6dbb6_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg26eYpr_Tf_text": "<p>The medical notes from their 2003 study showed these children shared the same symptoms with adults who looked far beyond their years…</p>",
        "gg3LqAAKT9R_text": "<p><strong>A month later they cried tears of joy, experiencing the sensation of skin that is smooth...fresh… and youthful once again.</strong></p>",
        "ggANQF96-3t_text": "<p><strong>What the researchers discovered about these women's skin was shocking.</strong></p>",
        "ggCRPVGVGxQ_text": "<p>And in one of the largest clinical studies ever conducted, 23 women ages 34 to 78 were analyzed for their response to anti-Progerin compounds.</p>",
        "ggD2H-JZ0tG_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s6bx1img.png",
        "ggGK2GnGpbi_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s6img.png",
        "ggGMWWeDiZm_text": "<p>Not only did the women's skin become softer, smoother and firmer...</p>",
        "ggIa8evHk0o_text": "<p>They had massive levels of an <strong>aging protein.</strong> And this isn’t a protein we eat. It's a protein molecule that builds up in our skin cells called <strong>Progerin</strong>.</p>",
        "ggJO2Nv8YuB_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s6bx1img.png",
        "ggJjHhWrEyv_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s6img.png",
        "ggKC6D9NXwF_text": "<p>Women who thought they could never get rid of aging skin, jowls, or turkey neck without surgery saw dramatic improvements.</p>",
        "ggi0_JJhhgZ_text": "<p>Looking at their transformations, I began to notice something that nobody else had seen:</p>",
        "ggkTyCiukPO_text": "<p>In 2012, the <strong>Advances in Dermatology Study </strong>showed that exposure to UVA rays from the sun significantly increases the amount of Progerin in our skin, which explains why excessive tanning prematurely ages us.</p>",
        "ggmEobjBzUd_text": "That's Why I Discovered Something Extraordinary When Studying Research From French Scientists Examining Children With Hutchinson-Gilford Syndrome - The \"Benjamin Button\" Disease That Causes Rapid Aging In Children.",
        "ggoK6BJKoyO_text": "<p>It looked and felt younger and healthier than it had in years.</p>",
        "ggr1gtYRUbN_text": "<p><strong>And because the skin cells were now fully enriched with these anti-Progerin compounds, they had a radiant glow as if they just came back from their honeymoon!</strong></p>",
        "ggvQi7ijQ1q_text": "<p>In 2012, the <strong>Advances in Dermatology Study </strong>showed that exposure to UVA rays from the sun significantly increases the amount of Progerin in our skin, which explains why excessive tanning prematurely ages us.</p>",
        "ggxRky0BdP4_text": "<p>You see, my own research and that of others has shown conclusively that Progerin levels are directly correlated with how quickly our skin ages.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607393614816870998"
    },
    "gp_section_607394200056497050": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "7cdffd0ad6d5175dffb7f1b30142f6837d8c6170fce77f05b3c43e5f06aecad5_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggDSDQTrKRz_text": "That's When I Realized - We Need TWO Things To Solve This Problem.",
        "ggObfPEeOx0_text": "<p>First, we need a way to reduce existing Progerin levels.</p>",
        "ggQ-whZi_7t_text": "<p><strong>The combination is the key...</strong></p>",
        "ggQlC2kabWI_text": "<p>When your skin has high levels of Progerin, a lot of the products you apply just sis on the surface. Your skin can't properly absorb and utilize beneficial ingredients because the aging protein is blocking cellular communication.</p>",
        "ggTGDVEDFbX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s10img.png",
        "ggVz8R4EHIa_text": "<p>And second, we need ingredients that can actually penetrate to support youthful skin function.</p>",
        "ggoy2kUeHCR_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s10img.png",
        "ggq0-ZeL52v_text": "<p>It's like an expensive cream with no way to penetrate. Or advanced ingredients that can't reach their targets.</p>",
        "ggujr2-VDDp_text": "<p>The two things have to work together -- just like a lock and key.</p>",
        "ggvFqun-tMa_text": "<p><strong>This is what most people don't understand about anti-aging treatments…</strong></p>",
        "ggvxs915RvZ_text": "<p>They're actually useless without both elements working together.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607394200056497050"
    },
    "gp_section_607396651660739158": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "20cc8095ddd157d9b3a6eff99fb5f21e303e38fd56e5b07bd22fad52900b545a_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-0VV79aIC_text": "<p>If it sounds incredible that all of this is associated with less Progerin and more Progeline in your skin, believe me, it is!</p>",
        "gg1N3-AKnLQ_text": "<p><strong>The most important one?</strong></p>",
        "gg2Q6xbi7Iw_text": "<p>We've been exposed to things that increase Progerin dramatically…including not just UV rays, but also environmental toxins, stress, and poor skincare products...</p>",
        "gg39edkJTii_text": "<p>&nbsp;but also environmental toxins, stress, and poor skincare products...</p>",
        "gg3VSjJQOPI_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s8img1_771e96a4-df37-43d1-8ba2-b55441681238.png",
        "gg6l30epRlK_text": "<p><strong>You guessed it, how much Progeline you have in your skin.</strong></p>",
        "gg7sUn2GE4V_text": "<p>The women using Progeline ALL had significantly improved skin appearance.</p>",
        "gg9LGWOie33_text": "<p>Well, when you look at studies on the effects of Progeline, you quickly realize how incredible this compound is...and the profound effect it can have on your appearance, your confidence, and your overall youthfulness.</p>",
        "ggAYU4T6yQW_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s8img3.png",
        "ggBHKMjGVRp_text": "<p>So having reduced Progerin levels means you have the skin structure of someone much younger (whether you actually are or not!)</p>",
        "ggBjyeY1Gu8_text": "<p>So that's what Progeline can do on a scientific level. But what does all that mean for you?</p>",
        "ggDd0wYZ-zh_text": "<p>Progerin dramatically…including not just UV&nbsp;rays,</p>",
        "ggHsR1UIaF4_text": "<p>When your skin is weak, these compounds create havoc on our appearance.</p>",
        "ggIH6pz3-Nk_text": "<p>I can tell you, both as a doctor and from treating thousands of patients, I now consider Progeline to be one of – if not THE – most important youth-boosting compounds for aging skin.</p>",
        "ggN7N46FGDT_text": "<p>When your skin is weak, these compounds create havoc on our appearance.</p>",
        "ggNTa89fW7f_text": "<p>And the women without Progeline continued to show signs of aging.</p>",
        "ggShNAgHsve_text": "<p>In 2003, French scientists published their groundbreaking study showing that the aging protein Progerin not only causes wrinkles... <strong>it affects our skin's entire structure.</strong></p>",
        "ggUDwaLwwy4_text": "<p>And we use products with ingredients far too often that actually accelerate aging... even though studies show every chemical-laden product you use damages your skin for years.</p>",
        "ggVnwn0wXbF_text": "So If Your Skin Was Like A Sagging Fabric,<br>Progeline Doesn't Just Temporarily Tighten The Surface... It Actually Reinforces The Entire<br>Structure From Within, Creating A Naturally Lifted, Youthful Appearance That Lasts!",
        "ggWOihVu22A_text": "<p><strong>Progeline </strong>was the difference between youthful and aging skin.</p>",
        "ggZaV5bfU0y_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s8img1_771e96a4-df37-43d1-8ba2-b55441681238.png",
        "ggdTWOEI5hU_text": "<p>We've been exposed to things that increase&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggi8E3iq_sC_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s8img2.png",
        "ggihDpBngo7_text": "<p>In a landmark study, 23 women ages 34 to 78 who were struggling with aging skin, sagging, and wrinkles had their results compared with younger women.</p>",
        "ggjOtLjtIhS_text": "<p><strong>This confirms separate research that Progeline could help reduce visible signs of aging by up to 22%.</strong></p>",
        "ggjUpkqTDMa_text": "<p>But Progeline fixes the damage.</p>",
        "gglbuUOdAF2_text": "<p>But it doesn't end there.</p>",
        "ggnAaj4q7OQ_text": "<p>In fact, there is almost no aspect of your appearance that age-fighting compounds don't play a massive role in.</p>",
        "ggqDQhm6Bdn_text": "<p><strong>And the more you have of it, the better you're going to look.</strong></p>",
        "ggySNzlvmsX_text": "<p>But it's not surprising when you remember what's happening in the average woman's skin...</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607396651660739158"
    },
    "gp_section_607398429357769626": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "8933d5f312376037c98eaec031cac5da890caa17d4d943407b2a42a814e0c724_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-7rFI8NP8_text": "<p>The \"anti-aging\" industry knows this is happening. But instead of addressing the root cause, they keep selling temporary fixes that just mask the problem.</p>",
        "gg-Ywhr1fFd_text": "<p>The Advances in Dermatology Study in 2012 showed something even more alarming: exposure to <strong>UVA rays from the sun significantly increases the amount of Progerin in our skin.</strong> Which is why excessive tanning prematurely ages us.</p>",
        "gg0LZtBCh-d_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img2.png",
        "ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_0": "<p>Their skin suddenly looking thin and crepey</p>",
        "ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_1": "<p>Loss of firmness happening rapidly</p>",
        "ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_2": "<p>Deep wrinkles forming seemingly overnight</p>",
        "ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_3": "<p>Sagging along the jawline and neck</p>",
        "ggAy1HlRgtH_childItem_4": "<p>A tired, aged appearance no matter what creams they try</p>",
        "ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_0": "<p>Adding more collagen (which can't penetrate deeply enough)</p>",
        "ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_1": "<p>Temporary plumping with hyaluronic acid</p>",
        "ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_2": "<p>Quick-fix tightening agents</p>",
        "ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_3": "<p>Protecting from sun damage</p>",
        "ggBDqb5qhkA_childItem_4": "<p>Masking imperfections with silicones</p>",
        "ggDghRP7tzj_text": "<p>And modern life makes this even worse. We're exposed to more environmental toxins, stress, and artificial ingredients than ever before -- all of which can accelerate Progerin production.</p>",
        "ggEi-UC_QMq_text": "<p>When they studied how women age, they discovered Progerin increases by 3% every year. By the time a woman reaches 40, her levels become so high it begins to show dramatically in her appearance.</p>",
        "ggEkbdvfi5c_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img1.png",
        "ggEnDX3ooFb_text": "<p>This wasn't just a coincidence. Their skin was actually functioning like that of a much younger person.</p>",
        "ggExhhDWLWe_text": "<p>When I looked closely at the research and compared it to what I was seeing in my own patients, I began to notice something that nobody else had seen...</p>",
        "ggHl01M2giV_text": "<p>Research from the <strong>Society of Cosmetic Chemists</strong> revealed something startling...</p>",
        "ggJwUlql5FY_text": "<p><strong>This Explains Why So Many Women Find:</strong></p>",
        "ggKnW-9rKsc_text": "<p><strong>But none of these address the real problem – rising Progerin levels that are aging us prematurely.</strong></p>",
        "ggN70CImHmA_text": "<p>Even worse, many expensive creams and treatments contain ingredients that can actually increase Progerin levels - making your skin age faster while promising to make you look younger!</p>",
        "ggNyq97XzV5_text": "<p>According to my research and that of other leading dermatologists, high Progerin levels are now considered the root cause of aging skin.</p>",
        "ggOndC3cyGS_text": "<p>The women who maintained youthful skin the longest all had something in common. Their skin cells showed remarkably lower levels of Progerin, similar to women decades younger.</p>",
        "ggUAj1-W08S_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img3.png",
        "ggWXj68qFWk_text": "<p>Looking At Skin Samples From My Patients, I Discovered Something That Nobody Else Had Noticed:</p>",
        "gg_fFEmlmop_text": "<p>But it's not surprising when you remember what's happening in most women's skin... We've been aging faster than ever before. Every day we're exposed to UV rays, pollution, stress, and skincare products that actually accelerate aging rather than prevent it.</p>",
        "ggbZCw8FFgD_text": "<p>You See, Most \"Solutions\" Focus On:</p>",
        "ggcAP1zJucy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img1.png",
        "ggf46UiPuCN_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img2.png",
        "ggfsfO2owSZ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9bx1bg.jpg",
        "ggh534PZbLV_text": "<p>Loss of firmness, wrinkles, thin crepey skin, jowls, turkey neck, and sagging... if it sounds incredible that all of these aging concerns are associated with just one protein, believe me, it is!</p>",
        "ggkcaQKNIQg_text": "<p>When your skin has high levels of Progerin, these factors create havoc on our appearance, making us look years or even decades older than we should.</p>",
        "ggoxbr_0le0_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9bx3bg.jpg",
        "ggtQfhBasUV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9bx2img.png",
        "ggtuQzix9i8_text": "<p>But here's what's most concerning...</p>",
        "gguCn0NkRPG_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s9img3.png",
        "gguejlQZWv8_childItem_0": "<p>When Progerin builds up, it destroys collagen</p>",
        "gguejlQZWv8_childItem_1": "<p>It makes our skin thinner</p>",
        "gguejlQZWv8_childItem_2": "<p>It eats away at elastin</p>",
        "gguejlQZWv8_childItem_3": "<p>It reduces firmness</p>",
        "gguejlQZWv8_childItem_4": "<p>It creates that loose, saggy appearance we all dread</p>",
        "ggvAls4Yr0I_text": "<p>That's why I refused to recommend any traditional anti-aging products to my patients.</p>",
        "ggvGcfqaX3X_text": "<p>Not to mention our modern lifestyle that increases Progerin, the “bad”production dramatically, letting it build up in our skin cells and causing us to age before our time.</p>",
        "ggw9OQm_-4__text": "So Having Higher Amounts Of Progeline In<br>Your Skin Means You Have The Skin Structure<br>Of Someone Decades Younger (Whether You Actually Are That Age Or Not!)",
        "ggx58kR-9bv_text": "<p><strong>Plus, studying these women's skin revealed something else extraordinary...</strong></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607398429357769626"
    },
    "gp_section_607399029579449242": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "f362c46b070d37a4dabc83e3198f922dfb16c91bf993a9bc4f98af1c213f09d9_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg1nkIJFGDK_text": "<p>You see, many skincare products actually contain ingredients that do nothing to address Progerin that’s building up in your skin with every passing year.</p>",
        "gg1uEbD9KWU_text": "<p><strong>Every effective anti-aging treatment contains specific compounds that seem to COUNTERACT the effects of Progerin.</strong></p>",
        "gg7RcLGLINb_text": "<p>To achieve this type of skin transformation yourself...</p>",
        "ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_0": "<p>It helps <strong>REDUCE </strong>existing Progerin levels</p>",
        "ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_1": "<p>It supports <strong>NATURAL </strong>collagen production</p>",
        "ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_2": "<p>It <strong>SUPPORTS </strong>skin firmness and elasticity</p>",
        "ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_3": "<p>It <strong>HELPS </strong>skin cells function optimally</p>",
        "ggH-IF72JEI_childItem_4": "<p>Most importantly, it helps <strong>PROTECT </strong>your skin against future aging</p>",
        "ggI5SrfopBc_text": "<p>These peptides help your body's natural repair processes work better.</p>",
        "ggNFZtz7xf7_text": "<p>In fact, when I looked closely at the research and compared it to my own clinical experience, I began to notice something remarkable.</p>",
        "ggO2KT9aTLg_text": "<p>Let me repeat this, because it's very important…</p>",
        "ggPj-4lNVeU_text": "<p>That's right. While most anti-aging products just sit on the surface, certain compounds can penetrate deep into the skin to fight this aging protein.</p>",
        "ggQFl8PaoGp_text": "<p>Aging skin occurs when Progerin builds up in our cells...but specific peptides exist that can help combat Progerin damage and actually help you maintain youthful skin.</p>",
        "ggQ_BbFw8ba_text": "<p>But none of these address the root cause – <strong>Progerin buildup in your skin cells.</strong></p>",
        "ggS4QpCDhUg_text": "<p>But when I studied the successful cases, I found something extraordinary...</p>",
        "ggU67xjylQm_text": "<p><strong>And the \"hero\" of your skin's youth is an incredible compound called Progeline.</strong></p>",
        "ggXOYUIFEV9_text": "<p>Research shows it does this by reducing Progerin levels by an astonishing 22%!</p>",
        "ggXnhWZIYU-_text": "<p>(That's the scientific name for it... but I like to<br>call this crucial anti-aging compound a \"skin youth factor.\")</p>",
        "gg_sKqDZmEM_text": "<p>That’s like rolling back the clock on your skin by 7-8 years!</p>",
        "ggdcORxlzMl_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s7bx2bg_852cf72e-2a5c-484b-a5e4-31e1f2bc42d1.png",
        "ggfHWDgQhXr_text": "<p>In your skin, this superhero ingredient is<br>in charge of many things:</p>",
        "ggfMfvQvs78_text": "<p>But most powerful of all... Progeline can actually strengthen your skin's repair processes.</p>",
        "ggi2cUQfYCu_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s7img.png",
        "ggk8rF0ewNp_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s7img.png",
        "ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_0": "<p>Adding more collagen</p>",
        "ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_1": "<p>Hydrating the skin</p>",
        "ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_2": "<p>Exfoliating dead cells</p>",
        "ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_3": "<p>Protecting from sun damage</p>",
        "ggn5LBBgigT_childItem_4": "<p>Plumping with hyaluronic acid<br>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggn8jXbVAZH_text": "<p>Progeline is a remarkable peptide. It's one of the most important age-fighting substances in dermatology.</p>",
        "ggpS471VD8v_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s7bx1bg.png",
        "ggqeGJPKoh2_text": "<p>Even more amazing, it's not the ingredients themselves that do it...</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607399029579449242"
    },
    "gp_section_607418420534706948": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "7dc2777e88d89d068555fabc649ed6319c43490859fae3906f058b47939b6aa0_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggMClzg_O4F_text": "<p><strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream is the first and ONLY formula on the market to combine powerful age-fighting peptides and ingredients.</strong></p>",
        "ggMagimsSAJ_text": "Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream.",
        "ggQDrQhDpos_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/My_fine_lines_are_barely_visible_and_my_skin_looks_firmer_and_more_lifted._My_face_finally_looks_youthful_again_the_confidence_is_real._Elena_58_Verified_Vitro_Customer_1_copy-Photoro.png",
        "gg__Xx8q_7d_text": "<p><strong>So today I'd like to introduce you&nbsp;to</strong></p>",
        "ggjdpirpak9_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo.png",
        "ggv6NrRn_Lh_background_desktop_image_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Generated_Image_February_20_2026_-_11_37PM_fcbc75b1-a92f-4b7a-bbe0-b39e4fc5d6d7.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607418420534706948"
