    "gp_section_607418478768423834": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "473af30d28ee7c89712f31ab2c1e592c6344e8eb318c1a28bc8b95b4428f0c14_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-1xcEe7Zb_text": "<p>Our lab discovered a way to turn these ingredients – including the breakthrough peptide Progeline – into a single, powerful cream...</p>",
        "gg-BZyaKsND_text": "<p>I'm going to tell you exactly how you can get Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream in just a moment, but first, let me explain how we achieved these incredible results...</p>",
        "gg2rwmhrbqK_text": "<p>Of all the beneficial ingredients you can get into your skin, my favorite is Progeline by far.</p>",
        "gg5Mfnronm-_text": "<p>Argireline</p>",
        "gg5sQtKn2G1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img1.png",
        "gg6YJF-YoSg_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/My_fine_lines_are_barely_visible_and_my_skin_looks_firmer_and_more_lifted._My_face_finally_looks_youthful_again_the_confidence_is_real._Elena_58_Verified_Vitro_Customer_1_copy-Photoro.png",
        "gg98HQ6wuQ-_text": "<p>Sends signals to replace lost collagen</p>",
        "ggB9CIykbEL_text": "<p>And do you know what I love most about this formula?</p>",
        "ggC-6c6pY-G_text": "<p>Matrixyl 3000</p>",
        "ggDZwW4D6CO_text": "<p>Sounds great! There's just one problem…</p>",
        "ggHmfe-lTl7_text": "<p>It's a non-surgical solution that doesn't require painful injections, expensive procedures, or risky operations of any kind.</p>",
        "ggJeGNpx0-a_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3licon2.png",
        "ggLKcWn-qRx_text": "<p>Best of all, it has no harsh chemicals, no artificial ingredients, and none of the toxins found in most anti-aging products.</p>",
        "ggOP9M0Vqql_text": "<p>This is a MAJOR innovation in the field of anti-aging skincare, which is why I believe the clinical results have been so extraordinary.</p>",
        "ggQojZiHBlW_text": "<p>Holds these youth-boosting results together</p>",
        "ggQrVcPjVe9_text": "<p>And for Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream, I chose the most advanced peptides on the planet...</p>",
        "ggRPJ3xfNb2_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3licon3.png",
        "ggRQaVoRpfN_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img1.png",
        "ggRmjE95fD-_text": "<p>And it's already helping women just like yourself achieve things they never thought were possible:</p>",
        "ggT82sEpCug_text": "<p>This advanced anti-aging formula is very unique. It has a sophisticated molecular structure that helps these compounds reach their cellular targets.</p>",
        "ggVRnK0JqCQ_text": "<p>But as I mentioned before, even the most powerful peptides would be useless without the right support ingredients... premium compounds that work together.</p>",
        "ggVsIPuaAq6_text": "<p>Reduces aging Progerin levels by an astonishing 22%</p>",
        "ggWmsMNFMY3_text": "<p>Our lab discovered a way to turn these ingredients – including the breakthrough peptide Progeline – into a single, powerful cream...</p>",
        "ggXygygDQoz_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img2.png",
        "ggYafxVdaqw_text": "<p>Ceramide</p>",
        "ggZxOkvOhUj_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3img.png",
        "gg_grqFw2t9_text": "<p>And it goes to work tightening and firming your skin after just the very first use.</p>",
        "ggbOQmGtgnd_text": "<p>You see, most anti-aging treatments you see in stores or online are made with ingredients that can't penetrate deeply enough... the same problem we had with finding a Progerin solution.</p>",
        "ggbachJNGIu_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx2img.png",
        "ggbachJNGIu_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/My_fine_lines_are_barely_visible_and_my_skin_looks_firmer_and_more_lifted._My_face_finally_looks_youthful_again_the_confidence_is_real._Elena_58_Verified_Vitro_Customer_1_copy-Photoro.png",
        "ggcHDFG7Sab_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3licon1.png",
        "ggebU32Pxyc_text": "<p>That's where our patented Anti-Progerin Complex comes in.</p>",
        "ggfz4oCnjhg_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img1.png",
        "ggjAMBfigwJ_text": "<p>In fact, these ingredients are specifically formulated to work at the deeper layers where Progerin accumulates!</p>",
        "ggj_mx-vatj_text": "<p>Helps prevent muscle movements that lead to wrinkles, like a gentle version of botox</p>",
        "ggkEhJugkSs_text": "<p>If it's a cheap anti-aging cream, very few – or perhaps even NONE – of those beneficial ingredients will effectively penetrate the skin!</p>",
        "ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_0": "<p>Sagging skin becoming dramatically firmer, with visible lifting results</p>",
        "ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_1": "<p>Deep wrinkles and fine lines finally becoming noticeably smoother</p>",
        "ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_2": "<p>\"Turkey neck\" and jowls visibly improving</p>",
        "ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_3": "<p>It reduces firmness</p>",
        "ggkZWAHyQat_childItem_4": "<p>Tired, aged appearance being replaced with a RADIANT glow...<br>the kind of youthful look you had decades ago, and the kind you can have again!</p>",
        "gglLQ1VcEHG_text": "<p>It's also been shown to reduce the appearance of jowls and <strong>\"turkey neck.\"</strong></p>",
        "ggldaZDZrsJ_text": "<p>That's because clinical studies have shown it to be effective in helping stop sagging, wrinkles, loss of firmness, and visible signs of aging.</p>",
        "ggmRsh0olZ5_text": "<p>These four key ingredients work as a line of defense AND restore your skin from within:</p>",
        "ggqOTnh48Db_text": "<p>So you'll see products advertised as having \"collagen\" or \"peptides\" or even \"stem cells\"...</p>",
        "ggqUpNPT80U_text": "<p>It's a healthy, dermatologist-formulated cream that is going to help you finally achieve the youthful appearance and confidence you DESERVE.</p>",
        "ggr-Lm5M12B_text": "<p>It's all thanks to these potent ingredients, which work because of what I call the<br>\"Anti-Progerin Complex”</p>",
        "ggrAZ1y_4XL_text": "<p>Progeline</p>",
        "ggs2obLP6iq_text": "<p>A cream you can apply yourself, every day, right in the comfort of your own home.</p>",
        "ggtH1IRtgXy_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13img2.png",
        "gguM0-_YYoi_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s13bx3licon4.png",
        "ggwS7OnCGUt_text": "<p>And it's in every jar of <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream.</strong></p>",
        "ggyE35Isi2M_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/NoBotox_NoFiller_JustBalm._2_copy.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607418478768423834"
    },
    "gp_section_607419063555064730": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "58c8c19993aec9df182aad3c8086b2949adc09ee2cd32f754ab56bb194f35bc6_1_1_0_0__1",
        "ggSDAmnenMG_text": "<p>The information presented on this website is not intended as specific medical advice and is not a substitute for professional treatment or diagnosis. These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Results can vary from person to person.</p>",
        "ggrV6cO86TF_text": "<p>© 2026 Vitro. All Rights Reserved.</p>"
