    "gp_section_607420054149005879": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "64dd2c33bd573a7c36f488c596180854765673713906e8f1e87396213efbd730_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg2WT8GZ0E1_text": "And The More Of These Youth-Boosting Compounds You Deliver Effectively To Your Skin, The More Dramatic Your Results Can Be.",
        "ggFgH9Fyzo-_text": "<p>That's why my research and development of this powerful formula took me months. We had to perfect not just the formula, but the delivery system as well.</p>",
        "ggIb9Ba5ABu_text": "<p>And I was determined to create something entirely new - something that would actually address the root cause of aging instead of just masking it temporarily.</p>",
        "gga6M-zsGpp_text": "<p>We made sure to use the absolute finest quality of natural peptides.</p>",
        "ggmdAQzHHAH_text": "<p>I partnered with the team at Vitro and spent months perfecting and testing a new age-defying formula.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607420054149005879"
    },
    "gp_section_607421094520947460": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "e9432f45683a3bd9aaa02812f06262530c4c5ad5e3408ac26b3fd824289914d2_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg2A5ZCOH6p_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s14bximg1.png",
        "gg3gtsISdmo_text": "<p><strong>Argireline</strong></p>",
        "gg5aXrsXJmX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s14bximg2.png",
        "gg7R2WcXJAF_text": "<p><strong>Ceramide</strong></p>",
        "gg7_l_8XDxK_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s14bximg3.png",
        "ggDTYJFRPWP_text": "<p><strong>Matrixyl 3000</strong></p>",
        "ggGQZI3F8rH_text": "<p>Argireline is truly remarkable. It helps prevent the muscle movements that lead to wrinkle formation - like a gentle version of Botox anyone can do at home. Instead of painful injections, this peptide works naturally to smooth expression lines. And finally, we added Ceramide.</p>",
        "ggJhDKzH7AF_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s14bximg2.png",
        "ggJhDKzH7AF_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s14bximg3.png",
        "ggRMwpiPqco_text": "<p><strong>Matrixyl 3000</strong> is a potent age-fighting peptide that sends signals to replace lost collagen. As collagen is responsible for keeping the skin strong and firm, this is crucial for maintaining youthful skin.</p>",
        "ggVna9B49FJ_text": "<p>It's a well-established fact that these peptides working together can help with:</p>",
        "ggZZoznT3tD_text": "A special form of peptide called<br>Matrixyl 3000.",
        "ggaiSBawPel_text": "<p>And I was determined to create something entirely new - something that would actually address the root cause of aging instead of just masking it temporarily.</p>",
        "gglKS1UJBgh_text": "<p>Ceramide is essential because it helps hold all these results together. It strengthens your skin's natural barrier, locking in moisture and helping maintain the firmness and elasticity these other ingredients create.</p>",
        "ggp-MwrLmsN_text": "<p>That's why my research and development of this powerful formula took me months. We had to perfect not just the formula, but the delivery system as well.</p>",
        "ggpohR0QMdN_childItem_0": "<p>Reducing appearance of wrinkles and fine lines</p>",
        "ggpohR0QMdN_childItem_1": "<p>Supporting firmer, more lifted skin</p>",
        "ggpohR0QMdN_childItem_2": "<p>Helping achieve a smoother texture</p>",
        "ggpohR0QMdN_childItem_3": "<p>Supporting natural collagen production</p>",
        "ggpohR0QMdN_childItem_4": "<p>Maintaining a more youthful appearance</p>",
        "ggqelpvvuVQ_text": "<p><strong>Then we added Argireline.</strong></p>",
        "ggsYkziEtr2_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s14bximg2.png",
        "ggx-AHSE1UU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s14bximg1.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607421094520947460"
    },
    "gp_section_607423020864111364": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "3a07727f00c6a956b0654aa3777bf4eda95c5110f4f9124e361ac881075a4c23_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg1pqLgwEjD_text": "<p>Then the <strong>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> was designed just for you.</p>",
        "gg4TdqUVdbO_text": "<p>This is where our Anti-Progerin Complex is different. Because it's formulated with ingredients with optimal molecular sizes, these ingredients can reach deeper levels of the skin effectively. For that reason, it's my anti-aging complex of choice.</p>",
        "gg6WAnzKVzP_text": "<p>But because you've read this entire report, and I know you're serious about fighting premature aging, I've asked our team to dramatically lower the cost of <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> for a brief period of time.</p>",
        "gg6YJNHad45_text": "<p>Now, at this time, I should point out that <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> is not necessarily for everyone.</p>",
        "gg7r5qvWMxe_text": "<p>And yes, this revolutionary formula is in every jar of <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream.</strong></p>",
        "ggAtnfjME9g_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s15bx2bg_2f4e9db2-032c-4fde-b9a8-b874965a52f5.jpg",
        "ggC0ekaF1Sg_text": "<p>So if you order today through this page, you can get MiamiMD's <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> for just <strong>$129.00.</strong></p>",
        "ggC4lZ-ixS1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/savebg.png",
        "ggJKKfuLCpl_text": "<p>Your Savings Reserved For&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggKVyvCpHsQ_text": "<p>They sit on the surface!</p>",
        "ggL3SvZSACX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s15img1.png",
        "ggLXl__3CJx_text": "<p>It's a proven, 4-part formula that will address sagging skin, deep wrinkles, and visible aging concerns in their tracks.</p>",
        "ggO5ccQiJpN_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s15img1.png",
        "ggQ945sDpQv_text": "<p>And nobody likes wasting expensive skincare products.</p>",
        "ggQFdnGDHyw_text": "<p><strong>Save</strong></p><p><span style=\"font-size:29px;\"><strong>$60</strong></span></p>",
        "ggQkNFU88SV_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#FFF7F7;\">&nbsp;00:00</span></p>",
        "ggTHYw4XC82_text": "<p>And nobody likes wasting expensive skincare products.</p>",
        "ggTRnJXbZLU_text": "SPECIAL REPORT-ONLY OFFER UP TO 30% OFF",
        "ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_0": "<p>Never go in the sun</p>",
        "ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_1": "<p>Always wear sunscreen</p>",
        "ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_2": "<p>Never make facial expressions</p>",
        "ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_3": "<p>Eat a perfect diet</p>",
        "ggUB7yaaAon_childItem_4": "<p>And have amazing genetics</p>",
        "ggVnk_O3v-3_text": "<p>And of course, they all work together to combat the aging effects of Progerin.</p>",
        "ggVtOnNe9Dt_text": "<p>You could try to source all these peptides<br>individually, but that would be extremely expensive and time-consuming...</p>",
        "ggWe4MqEErU_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s15bx1bg.jpg",
        "ggYVkKshpTU_text": "<p>So if you order today through this page, you can get Vitro's <strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> for just <strong>$129.00.</strong></p>",
        "ggZYZvkjlD0_text": "<p>Now, let's talk about how you can get <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> for yourself today.</p>",
        "gg_k2dXBSPj_text": "<p>So if you'd rather have this incredible formula measured perfectly, and know that every batch was tested for safety, effectiveness, and potency...</p>",
        "ggd6HPVOQMR_text": "<p><strong>That's an instant savings of $60.00!</strong></p>",
        "ggeDFwdKIEs_text": "<p>Then you may truly be one of the few women who do not have high Progerin levels... and are already experiencing the benefits of naturally youthful skin.</p>",
        "ggew1kLS4oE_text": "<p>If you already have what I call \"Perfect Skin Habits\",<br>meaning you:</p>",
        "gggy7rIQ8IZ_text": "<p>For instance, collagen creams are super popular and contain beneficial ingredients. But sometimes if you use too much, you're just wasting product because it can't penetrate deeply enough.</p>",
        "ggiPAPSYmtP_text": "<p>When <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> is available in stores, my distributor tells me it will retail for around $189.00... a great price when you consider how expensive and time-consuming it is to get these potent age-fighting ingredients and peptides.</p>",
        "ggj5dUkPDYU_text": "<p>Then we've created an easy way for you to obtain <strong>Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream</strong> for yourself.</p>",
        "ggj7jOZHW3A_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/timer.png",
        "ggpBxiHMJwQ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/My_fine_lines_are_barely_visible_and_my_skin_looks_firmer_and_more_lifted._My_face_finally_looks_youthful_again_the_confidence_is_real._Elena_58_Verified_Vitro_Customer_1_copy-Photoro.png",
        "ggvCGnjY8oY_text": "<p>But remember, most anti-aging formulas have one big problem...</p>",
        "ggvY7UmQ_-1_text": "<p>However, if you’re like most women who know they have some sun damage, can see visible lines and wrinkles, and don't eat a perfect diet…</p>",
        "ggw9cD5i4rX_text": "<p>And when you combine our breakthrough Progeline with Matrixyl 3000, Argireline, and Ceramide – you get what I now consider to be the most powerful, all-in-one anti-aging treatment we've ever created, bar none.</p>",
        "ggzlwR45GSn_text": "<p><strong>That's an instant savings of $60.00!</strong></p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607423020864111364"
    },
    "gp_section_607423893581333402": {
