        "checksum": "9584021ae0c209a6dd8e4f3ba57595251eaa63707ef771aa5458d7c67f34bfe6_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg9X9K8DeBY_text": "<p>I've tried to do my part by creating this online report. Now, we need to spread the word.</p>",
        "ggBTNm2HZpe_text": "<p>As you know, it's one of the greatest threats to maintaining a youthful appearance, and most people at risk have no idea that this aging protein is so directly linked to sagging skin, wrinkles, and many other visible signs of aging.</p>",
        "ggGI8M6OkHQ_text": "<p>My email address is support@trymiamimd.com. Seeing and hearing how science changes people's lives is probably the greatest joy I experience as a doctor.</p>",
        "ggLzRU5G2r__text": "<p>When they DO sell out, this offer will be taken down immediately and <strong>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> will return to its regular price of <strong>$189.00.</strong></p>",
        "ggYDcVPTNT6_text": "<p>1</p>",
        "ggZfgTalwKL_text": "<p>First, when you begin using Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm and you experience what I did – the dramatic improvement in appearance, the firmer skin, the surge of confidence – write in to tell me about the wonderful changes you see.</p>",
        "ggckfr3MT-n_text": "<p>2</p>",
        "gget3nUAHPo_text": "<p>And second – and this is just as important – please tell your friends and loved ones about the dangers of Progerin buildup in our skin.</p>",
        "ggfSE_gbYtT_text": "<p><strong>This is an incredible opportunity, and if you take it, I only ask 2 things:</strong></p>",
        "ggjme2cS9pL_text": "<p>But remember, this offer is only available to report readers through this page – and it's only available until supplies run out.</p>",
        "ggqT2ofjRHx_text": "<p>And supplies WILL sell out.</p>"
