        "gg-2BJbx0CI_text": "<p>Imagine the feeling of applying <strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> for the first time, knowing the formula was scientifically tested for years using the most advanced age-fighting, wrinkle-reducing technology available.</p>",
        "gg-xyzpH9iD_text": "<p>Free Shipping</p>",
        "gg0ebY4zrBd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s17bxprd.png",
        "gg0oWHaeK1e_text": "<p>You can call us 7 days a week at <span style=\"color:#007FFF;\">844-829-8772</span> with questions about your order, to hear about our lab...or just to tell us the big changes you've noticed since using <strong>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm !</strong></p>",
        "gg202eHqw-0_label": "<p>CLAIM DISCOUNT</p>",
        "gg2Btb_8ik1_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s17img2.png",
        "gg4O6lTE3jv_label": "<p>CLAIM DISCOUNT</p>",
        "gg5KhB8qsi4_text": "<p>Free Shipping</p>",
        "gg72U-q2FCL_text": "<p><strong>Now, I'd like to get serious for a moment and talk about what's going to happen if you DON'T start making some real changes to your skincare routine today...</strong></p>",
        "gg8Q_dh-xx-_text": "Vitro 90-Day<br>Money-Back Guarantee.",
        "ggAIuO5F2cq_text": "<p>I've seen minor skin aging concerns turn into much more serious conditions.</p>",
        "ggCJt7jlnth_text": "<p>When our Anti-Progerin Complex begins to take effect in your skin, you could feel what I and other users do – the pleasant sensation of firming, that feeling of pure confidence and radiance. Like the years have been brushed aside, and everything is suddenly transformed.</p>",
        "ggCS_5_4DVL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo2.png",
        "ggCxlLwUymi_text": "<p>When you order a pack of 3 jars of K-Beauty Calcium Balm, you'll pay only $43 per jar.</p>",
        "ggD0RoJmLbw_text": "<p><i><strong>\"I didn't know my skin could still look this good again!\"</strong></i></p>",
        "ggDXKnsXcgg_text": "<p>So we've created multi-pack options, to help you get some really big savings.</p>",
        "ggD_7aX6zTl_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo2.png",
        "ggEJ_JFciN8_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/new_truck_icon_f198daf3-b91a-476d-8262-2185f07dc021.png",
        "ggF0Lu6qs2__text": "<p>Yet it provides far more dramatic results – leaving your skin looking firmer and more youthful all day, without any temporary tightening or</p><p>artificial effects.</p>",
        "ggFKDBcIg8H_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s17img3.png",
        "ggFNMz5GaeO_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s17img1.png",
        "ggFdAXsa_Qg_text": "K-Beauty Calcium Balm",
        "ggGBr65RenX_text": "<p>Best of all, every jar of <strong>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> comes with our</p>",
        "ggG_EWNAOdP_text": "<p>When this batch is sold out, the offer will be removed immediately and K-Beauty Calcium Balm will return to its regular price of $360.00.</p>",
        "ggH12gCxzN4_text": "<p><strong>So click the “Claim Discount” button below, and let’s get started.</strong></p>",
        "ggH3BL4clGD_text": "<p>4.77 Stars based on 1291 Reviews</p>",
        "ggIxA28Yop0_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s17img2.png",
        "ggKzIjbsp99_text": "<p>With today's discount, you can pay as little as $40.00 per jar to have the age-fighting, youth-boosting power of our \"Anti-Progerin Complex\", as well as the firming power of reduced wrinkles, and so much more from the 4 unique ingredients and peptides in the cream.</p>",
        "ggOa9W88li9_text": "<p>When you get to our order page, you'll see order options for <strong>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> on the right side of the page. If you see options for our special 3 and 6 bottle packages, then we still have some of those packages in stock, and the extra savings are still available.</p>",
        "ggPlZ_EwS8p_text": "<p>4.77 Stars based on 1291 Reviews</p>",
        "ggQRbTx6CrM_text": "<p>Free Shipping</p>",
        "ggQn_ZDPXV2_text": "<p>So please, if you want to feel the dramatic effects of this groundbreaking age-fighter, click the \"<strong>Claim Discount</strong>\" button below, while there's still time available and we have some jars left in stock.</p>",
        "ggSD_PZqj4C_text": "<p>And if you order a package of 6 jars, you'll save even more.</p>",
        "ggTB3qeQBbz_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo2.png",
        "ggTB3qeQBbz_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo2.png",
        "ggTjqQV2u_a_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Untitled_design_54.png",
        "ggU1ARTkMAB_text": "<p>I've seen patients who didn't handle their early signs of aging get worse &amp; worse, ruining their confidence and quality of life.</p>",
        "ggU1aO8tHbY_text": "<p>Our website is fully protected by the latest security technology, so your order is 100% secure.</p>",
        "ggUgLbgIvqV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/mbbg.jpg",
        "ggUszQGNFuc_text": "<p>That's why I'm urging you to take action today and make a positive change in your appearance.</p>",
        "ggUw5vYbVuI_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/mbbg.jpg",
        "ggUw5vYbVuI_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/mbbg_-_Copy_9b43cd0a-0e2c-4ff5-8351-f30d3ecd63c5.jpg",
        "ggVJ_oYZpHA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/stars.png",
        "ggYJ9BYbFgX_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/new_truck_icon_f198daf3-b91a-476d-8262-2185f07dc021.png",
        "ggZGn9lRcCi_text": "<p>Yes, you could make some radical changes to your lifestyle – dramatically avoiding all sun exposure, never making facial expressions, starting extensive cosmetic procedures – but these changes are very difficult to maintain and are also very expensive.</p>",
        "ggaAcj8HAzL_text": "<p>In fact, I bet after your first time using<strong> K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong>,<br>you'll say to yourself exactly what I did:</p>",
        "ggaxXWfrFOx_text": "K-Beauty Calcium Balm",
        "ggblmnsYHqh_text": "<p>And our warehouse is based in the USA with a team of friendly customer service specialists standing by if you have any questions.</p>",
        "ggdqCuZjkrP_text": "<p>And the reason we have so many happy women in our community is because when they start using<br><strong>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong>, they end up asking for quite a bit more...not just for themselves, but for friends and family too.</p>",
        "ggg3av6NbI6_text": "<p>So click the \"Claim Discount\" button below right now to find out if these options are still available. If we do still have stock available from this batch, you'll see a SUPPLY UPDATE on the product page with current inventory. I encourage you to act now if you're serious about your appearance and maintaining youthful skin.</p>",
        "gggbWvmuhcq_text": "<p>These are not problems that just go away on their own.</p>",
        "ggh0KP28z2C_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s17bxprd.png",
        "gghCkcx_vSj_text": "<p>And because you've made it this far, and because you're serious about improving your appearance and confidence, we've got some special packages available to help you even more.</p>",
        "ggiFfhVkJj__srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s17img1.png",
        "ggjMDgjc9Xi_text": "<p>You see, most women fall in love with <strong>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> after just their first week of use...myself included. In fact, a lot of women report seeing and feeling changes within the first 21 days – a number that shocks even me.</p>",
        "ggl8MPswthd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/stars.png",
        "ggmX5xNuTTW_text": "<p>The sagging you're dealing with right now, the deep wrinkles, the tired appearance...</p>",
        "ggqAeWtqsCP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo2.png",
        "ggrRCfEUTII_label": "<p>CLAIM DISCOUNT</p>",
        "ggsDIMiItyf_text": "<p>But remember, <strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> is not available in stores and our formula is incredibly difficult to produce.</p>",
        "ggv-NaejusZ_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/new_truck_icon_f198daf3-b91a-476d-8262-2185f07dc021.png",
        "ggv7xz-BmxZ_text": "<p>Now, unless you're one of the tiny fraction of women who have perfect genetics and no signs of aging, the reality is that your skin will continue to deteriorate as you get older if you do nothing to stop it.</p>",
        "ggvm1B5aa10_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Untitled_design_54.png",
        "ggw6UXpj9xi_text": "<p>Yes, that means you can use the entire jar, and if you don’t experience ALL of the benefits…just send it back, and we’ll happily return every cent. No questions asked. Even if the jar is empty.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That’s how confident we are in this groundbreaking formula, so I&nbsp;want you to use it all…and experience the incredible transformation yourself.</p>",
        "ggx6ElRf-8o_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s17img3.png",
        "ggyNOO26k1l_text": "<p>That's $60 off the retail price of $189.00... and you'll get free shipping with your order today!</p>",
        "ggyVbCOJjeD_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Generated_Image_February_22_2026_-_7_34PM-Photoroom_1.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607438910045291268"
