        "ggc2lFlpyzh_text": "<p>Don't forget, you'll get significantly deeper discounts on larger packages — up to $60.00 instantly off the retail price — if you act right now.</p>",
        "ggdVe0nDQro_text": "<p>I want you to feel – and SEE – your transforming appearance every morning when you look in the mirror.</p>",
        "gggGbGbtMDE_text": "<p>Try it for a full 60 days... and if you're unsatisfied with the results for any reason whatsoever, you'll get a complete refund of your money.</p>",
        "ggnIt0UGT_P_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo2.png",
        "ggpCvFQ5EGa_text": "<p>I want you to feel great when you look in the mirror and to make aging skin concerns a thing of the past.</p>",
        "ggrDnZN7rIm_text": "<p>One application per day of this cream can have such a remarkable impact on so many areas of your appearance. I recommend you use it day and night to get the full benefits.</p>",
        "ggy02iVnhVV_text": "<p>I want you to feel the surge of confidence that comes with this formula.</p>",
        "ggyVcKZU5md_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/stars.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-607439463626310554"
    },
    "gp_section_607459536441180758": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "9449687c56da5eee2dcfb02756af61d3cf9940b16e1829a20c76931c3a601565_1_1_0_0__1",
        "gg-KRt-yXy2_text": "<p>You'll know it's working when people start asking what you've \"had done\"...when friends want to know your secret... when your spouse can't stop commenting on how amazing and refreshed you look.</p>",
        "gg1RwHKhJVq_text": "<p>But, of course, as a dermatologist I know that no skincare works for everyone. There's always a very small segment of the population who may be sensitive to certain ingredients.</p>",
        "gg6aKBfunzp_text": "<p><strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm </strong>utilizes powerful Progeline so you can build stronger, healthier skin... which means your peptides and active ingredients cannot just sit on the surface. When your anti-aging ingredients penetrate deeply... THAT'S when they can do their best work.</p>",
        "gg7JpEa9n_J_label": "<p>CLAIM DISCOUNT</p>",
        "gg9GX35IYrM_text": "<p>*Every individual is unique. As such, your results can and will vary.</p>",
        "ggDfJJmNRP0_text": "<p>However, I'm experienced enough in dermatology to know that people are different. An individual's skin can react very differently to identical compounds.</p>",
        "ggEO-DcoyVw_text": "<p>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm contains only high quality ingredients that work effectively for all skin types. The content of every batch is tested at my own facility.</p>",
        "ggFhBsw__x4_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/new_truck_icon_f198daf3-b91a-476d-8262-2185f07dc021.png",
        "ggHIPpLOc2c_text": "<p>Dr. Manjula Jegasothy</p>",
        "ggHIQR3gVdd_text": "<p>In fact, if there's any reason at all you're unsatisfied after a full 90 days of use, I'll return your investment.</p>",
        "ggHpo0BZ-xw_text": "<p>To your beauty and happiness,</p>",
        "ggHsc-0lZDv_text": "<p>Plus, the big difference between <strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> and other anti-aging formulas is that I chose the ingredients based on clinical results. Look, I'm a board-certified dermatologist with 20 plus years experience and extensive clinical research background, so I brought that expertise to the table. This formula gets real results because it's got proven ingredients at the right concentrations.</p>",
        "ggHzoPiZGps_text": "<p>You'll find detailed information on the website about the full list of ingredients in this cutting-edge formula, about myself and my medical credentials, and everything you need to know about the product.</p>",
        "ggJPyBPlDCb_text": "<p>So, not only does it provide visible results…it helps maintain those improvements over time. That means YOU get to experience a dramatic transformation in firmness, a remarkable 'lifting effect,' even better skin texture, and amazing youthful radiance.</p>",
        "ggJdzonuPCZ_text": "<p>However, the great news is this.. if the formula doesn't get results for you, I'm going to give you your money back.</p>",
        "ggJeefOKuYx_text": "<strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong>",
        "ggLW6E4fPE9_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo2.png",
        "ggLW6E4fPE9_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo2.png",
        "ggLnUY-YJZa_childItem_0": "<p><strong>\"I&#039;ve seen &#039;anti-aging&#039; products advertised... how is Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm different?\"</strong></p>",
        "ggLnUY-YJZa_childItem_1": "<p><strong>\"Will it work for my skin type?\"</strong></p>",
        "ggLnUY-YJZa_childItem_2": "<p><strong>\"How long until I see results?\"</strong></p>",
        "ggLnUY-YJZa_childItem_3": "<p><strong>\"What if it doesn't work for me?\"</strong></p>",
        "ggMgxSsldbZ_text": "<p>Second, many other anti-aging products don't address Progerin — and that's absolutely crucial. We talked earlier about how this protein causes aging all over your face and neck... creating serious problems, including sagging and wrinkles. So, <strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> specifically targets Progerin. It also has no irritating ingredients, another \"toxic skincare addition\" I tell everyone to avoid.</p>",
        "ggNVvY6ye_g_text": "<p>Again, my reputation is on the line here... I want every single person who comes to Vitro to have a completely positive experience. It's my name on the label, and I've come too far to risk that.</p>",
        "ggNxcsOJ3Mv_text": "<p>First, most anti-aging products have added fragrances or artificial ingredients. Both are terrible for your skin, and they can actually accelerate aging. <strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> has no harsh chemicals or artificial ingredients whatsoever.</p>",
        "ggOcs2E_8JV_text": "<p>Most importantly, though — other formulas are designed only for temporary results. Our <strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> also provides immediate benefits — but it does SO much more, too.</p>",
        "ggPKU4aLySH_text": "<p>I've even seen very effective treatments have little to no effect on certain patients.. and it's all just down to their individual skin dynamics. So, even though our users rave about the incredible changes they see when using Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream – there are going to be some cases with fewer results.</p>",
        "ggQ8_lzq5rL_text": "<p>To see the full list of ingredients, concentrations, and product facts... just click the \"Claim Discount\" button below for more information.</p>",
        "ggRM7vWF1qX_text": "<p>It also means any other MiamiMD formula you're currently using will be enhanced as well. Because when those ingredients work together, it allows your skin to use them much more effectively.</p>",
        "ggTn91SxTwZ_label": "<p>CLAIM DISCOUNT</p>",
        "ggUBDfuJMl__text": "<p>It's been a pleasure spending this time with you today, and I hope you'll take action now. Just click the button below to start transforming your appearance and confidence!</p>",
        "ggW_4x3S1rP_text": "<p>This is what I'm talking about.. the real meaning of having youthful, beautiful skin!</p>",
        "ggWyYeDPdcS_text": "<p>You'll feel better about your appearance, and others will start to notice too. After your morning application, you'll start to notice how much younger you look in the mirror.</p>",
        "ggZ45hbY3EO_text": "<p>Another great question, one we get all the time. Look, as a dermatologist, I believe that everyone can benefit from the age-defying, skin-firming ingredients in this formula.</p>",
        "gg_-sOTV3wJ_text": "<p>Of course, there's only one way to really find out if K-Beauty Calcium Balm &nbsp;will work for you... and that's to try it for yourself.</p>",
        "ggdKjEsaSvs_text": "<p>And my formula contains none of the harsh elements that typically cause reactions in sensitive skin. Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm is fragrance-free, artificial ingredient-free, harsh chemical-free, and irritant-free, making it suitable for even the most delicate skin.</p>",
        "ggdrSK2dMPW_text": "<p>And the results from this breakthrough formula get better over time. This is a lasting transformation... because it's the kind of improvement your skin is supposed to be getting.</p>",
        "ggf7M2VUTex_label": "<p>CLAIM DISCOUNT</p>",
        "gggXp5vJquz_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/Untitled_design_54.png",
        "gggx7S2Oros_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/s17bxprd.png",
        "ggh5xN_KCeT_text": "<p>Also, <strong>K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> is not just an anti-aging cream at all. It's really a 4-in-1 formula that can help boost firmness, smooth wrinkles, lift sagging, and solve aging concerns like nothing else can. It's a complete package with the right stuff that works.</p>",
        "ggi_SuQbskH_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/sig.png",
        "ggkL3AN1ie-_text": "<p>Now, if you have some questions... that's very common. Let me take a few moments to answer some of the most commonly asked questions about Age Defying Lift &amp; Firm Cream.</p>",
        "ggksS6Z_zxb_text": "<p>Before I developed this formula, I looked at the other products out there. And I saw huge problems with every one of them... so much so, I refused to recommend any of them to my patients. Here's why...</p>",
        "ggkz-ZHtStf_text": "<p>Free Shipping</p>",
        "ggl3eMsvrlH_text": "<p>So, please...simply click the \"Claim Discount\" button below and get started – risk-free – right now.</p>",
        "ggnF433vUi2_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/logo2.png",
        "ggpafkBf6lX_text": "<p>As a dermatologist, I'm putting my reputation on the line with this product — so you can be sure I go to great lengths to make sure every jar is absolutely safe for all skin types.</p>",
        "ggqnpuHH7CB_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/stars.png",
        "ggrCxDEnDcD_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "ggsA-Bh3iYu_text": "<p>So...try <strong>Vitro K-Beauty Calcium Balm</strong> for two full months. If you don't see truly remarkable results – less sagging, reduced wrinkles, smoother texture, firmer skin, and better overall appearance – I'll give you your money back, and that's my personal guarantee.</p>",
        "ggsk6b5qmTv_text": "<p>So consult your doctor if you have extremely sensitive skin. And if you want to return it for any reason at all, simply contact our US-based customer support team for an immediate refund.</p>",
        "ggt8MGmI5Zu_text": "<p>Most women report feeling a noticeable tightening effect within days.</p>",
        "ggvLLqY_aQ3_text": "<p>Great question. The best thing about this formula is that you're going to see and feel it working very quickly.</p>",
        "ggvVZ7BEGyB_text": "<p>4.77 Stars based on 1291 Reviews</p>",
        "ggxoMyvjAxR_text": "<p>I made a pledge when I developed the Vitro line: I will never sell any product I wouldn't personally recommend to my patients.</p>",
        "ggzr4YyQfnx_text": "<p>You'll notice your skin feeling firmer and looking smoother right away. Within days, your complexion should appear more radiant and youthful.</p>"
      },
